Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.13,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.34,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.14,0:00:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.42,0:01:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.95,0:01:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac175年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的领导人被暗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部钢弹被派往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本应是为了报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但由于OZ在宇宙的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非摆出支配的姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是处处以协调为先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是，卫星接受OZ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在支配地球和宇宙的进程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.61,0:01:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹被视作\N叛徒的象征给孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无家可归的钢弹及其驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不断转变的时代里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.32,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以存在意义为赌注继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…宇宙服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙服是攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快制止它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,障碍…要清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十话\N潜入月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大量钢弹特殊合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被运进月面基地的工场里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是为了制造新型机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过最近的连续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连我的身体也支持不了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你不能说得婉转一点的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你代替我上学就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用你的名字办理入学手续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?这玩笑真过份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字在这里\N多引人注目也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就乖乖地等待身体痊愈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使叫他别勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙也一定不会听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去到月球后才决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抢夺，还是破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重力是地球的六分之一的月球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的居住空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不适合的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙卫星的完成期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类在月球进行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各种研究设施\N和巨大工场的建设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.26,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来，月球更发展为\N宇宙观光地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招待由地球来的游客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在联合的压迫前相当繁荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于OZ成功把联合军解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球被准许继续作为观光地经营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事被人们当作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙恢复和平的预兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星间的移动也变得自由了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的OZ看来在尽力诱惑宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了讨好卫星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ要用尽各种怀柔手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦令他们信任之后就简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,资源和劳动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会在一瞬间被OZ吸干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要造出些难驯的悍马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令OZ为难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[麦丘留士]的防御系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[拜叶特]的主体组合后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致就成形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成只是时间的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们没打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远照OZ的吩咐工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然事情已经交由蕾蒂‧安负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来会从卫星市民里挑选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶这两部机动战士的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许会有趣起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何，不会那么顺利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛不会采取\N那么转折的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那个人会更加直接了当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，我们完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ追求的强力机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后证明它们也能消灭OZ啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ说想在宇宙建立国家吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从联合的支配体制解放出来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民间性也好，卫星之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球的交流也重新开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这的确是OZ的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但无必要连卫星今后的行政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也听从OZ的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.56,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，从现在卫星的规模来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信不作为一个国家会更奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，但问题就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要工业由军事技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和机动战士的生产组成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，卫星代表团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然对那文件有疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看过联合胡乱使用\N军备后的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会认为机动战士的生产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等同死亡商人的行为吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援OZ的国家想要宇宙的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只为了用作军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为主张和平\N的卫星不会接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在被认为是制衡力就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那段期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙里不够的东西\N也会齐备了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙里不够的东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正确的秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.45,0:07:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，要你们久等，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位已经看过手上的文件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有宇宙卫星\N被地球认为是威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因相信也在于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的非主流组织里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.46,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为建立国家\N是有意义的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，对主要工业有问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在需要军备\N作为制衡力的想法下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界不可能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们从过去的历史里学到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星有可能确立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球分开的新秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技术力成为瑰宝\N令我们非常自豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不可以想及生产军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在我心里，战争已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ是军事组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们努力平息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球上重覆着的纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某段时期，地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾经像各位一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以不寻求军事力量\N的和平为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，那里诞生了什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要胡乱战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，失去战斗姿态的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能道出人类的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被男人的那种姿态迷住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到OZ把它复原至这地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不可以把钢弹交给OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那问题我想问你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深夜潜入来装炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是等闲之辈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先把那个引爆器交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经有必死之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会交出钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种爆炸下毫无损伤!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不能由衷地高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不愧是钢弹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!真胡来啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被OZ发觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才那个女人帮了我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们死也要夺回\N卡特尔少爷的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧部队出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在钢弹04的机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易潜入来却弄成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚布度的作战没好结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?你说了什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点带卡特尔少爷的钢弹来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么? 奥达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!离远一点战斗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好不容易才抢到这部运输机啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们原定OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会帮我们把钢弹修复完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想不到这么快就行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚夫马特!快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!很完美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功逃脱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?为何停下来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止无谓的战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!是那个女人的声音!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!是奥达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不是敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果是我认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这情形，他会破坏钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认识的人觉得破坏是悲哀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想设法修好它\N令他高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也是钢弹的朋友吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是中东的马格亚那队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这部钢弹交给我们处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子看来也是好孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的朋友也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去把另一个好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丢下的东西捡回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是卫星为了自卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日在宇宙进行的有意义影象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被挑选出来的年轻志愿兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将会肩负宇宙的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何所有人都照OZ的说话做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻人们在假设为实战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射击测试里取得好成绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，在全体的前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们准备了多个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假设为敌人的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对手是模拟弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但被击中会有很强的冲击啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了!迎击开始!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终只是新人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.10,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?\N那家伙…是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是一号机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演习完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一号机驾驶员，核对名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶者，特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，特洛瓦‧巴顿有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行过多少次模拟也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没理由能在初次实战里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出那种回避动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.03,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在某处受过训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是相当高度的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,履历已经完全检查过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，那是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，他有潜在的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以来无用武之地的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他有可能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派来破坏OZ的特工…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，马上查明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追加演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把下一个目标完全毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!他果然是钢弹的驾驶员!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那支雷射炮借给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是钢弹特殊合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以里欧的来福枪不会有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,产生地球和卫星的误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑起战乱的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在即将被祈求和平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星市民亲手毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请静心欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.31,0:14:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，死神，不要轻易被毁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次演习，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脑波和心跳也完全无变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是完美的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，还有若干疑问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他拥有参加OZ的姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有天份的人会了解OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…眼泪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型的机动战士吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,设计中的零件还很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一号机练习生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校要见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在那里等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校，很危险!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还有可能是钢弹的驾驶员!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我独自和他见面看来比较好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他来是想了解OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不见他是没礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同是爱护宇宙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交谈起来也会起劲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥尔特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何害怕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗快要结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.65,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸会，我叫蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个人就是蕾蒂‧安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ宇宙军最高指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安上级特校吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾经以工程用机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修补卫星的外壁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在演习的成绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令OZ的现役士兵很惊奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.10,0:17:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为我有天份作为士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我被录用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起令宇宙和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想自己的本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能为打倒联合宇宙军效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没想过宇宙的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.32,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我认为我是适合OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,适合OZ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢一面摆出友好姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面想支配宇宙的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们会评为卑鄙的手段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那适合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配?卑鄙的手段?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙小人被认同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校你去冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，特校，这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校被骗，我也不会被骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校命令你两小时后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行OZ新型机动战士的测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但特校她现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿起军服的\N蕾蒂‧安特校很坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.38,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她或许不会放过可疑的你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是特列斯大人的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,征召得比想像中快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这五人是从卫星市民里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,选拔出来的驾驶员候补生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中，特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是最优秀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他能驾御任何机动战士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.76,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两部机动战士\N不能轻易操纵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来造得比钢弹好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麦丘留士80%，拜叶特50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何须要开发不同的类型?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两部机是\N基于战斗的基本姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进攻和防守达至极限时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有何结果而制造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特有一支能源炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的体积会尽量保留机动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麦丘留士有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵挡那支能源炮的防护罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两部机战斗会有何结果?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是优秀驾驶员驾驶的取胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士的性能竞争是无聊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以驾驶者的能力来决定胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ推荐的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好聪明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦特士，你闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，是他将要驾驶的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我批准发问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，今日会展示什么测试?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麦丘留士的防御方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是能造出电场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.36,0:20:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵挡敌人能源的革新系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特方面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特还未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未注入能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事!?拜叶特动了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开动麦丘留士的防护罩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.33,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样?我的兵器优秀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他来取我们的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.93,0:22:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.93,0:22:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.93,0:22:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.93,0:23:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.43,0:23:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有部白色机动战士接近卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当查明那是杰克斯驾驶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.70,0:23:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安命令特洛瓦和希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.47,0:23:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.74,0:23:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，受了伤的卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.70,0:23:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到亲切的温拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他爸爸在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.51,0:23:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独自承担人们的责难和咒骂
